Interface ConfigPackageImpl.Literals

Enclosing class:
ConfigPackageImpl
public static interface ConfigPackageImpl.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
